  <title>DATA MODELING</title>
  <p>Part 2 of this book concerns graphical modeling in general, and entity-relationship diagrams in particular.  The diagram below shows the strong dependencies between chapters; chapters will assume knowledge introduced in earlier chapters as implied by the graph.  The dotted outlines indicate chapters from other sections of the book.</p>
